  <brief_title>Anterior Component Separation Versus Posterior Component Separation for Repair of Large Ventral Hernias</brief_title>
  <official_title>Anterior Component Separation Versus Posterior Component Separation for Repair of Large Ventral Hernias: a Prospective Cohort Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
